videos.title: The ULTIMATE GUIDE for Bristly Bill's Champion Deck
videos.description:
This Mono Green Landfall Brawl deck is available in the MTG Arena store as a Champion Deck for the Brawl format with Bristly Bill, Spine Sower as the commander.  Is it worth the gems?  Can it win games? Let's find out.

Decklist - https://moxfield.com/decks/A0mTjRWXQ0y51JU4i-ULdw

Decklist (Upgraded) - https://moxfield.com/decks/N12-M4LcQ0WGbjzRFJPZeQ

Sponsors

Dragon Shield Coupon Code CGB5 - https://dragonshield.com/?ref=CGB
